### Test Auto Status Update Feature
### File này dùng để test API với REST Client extension trong VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3002
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create a new task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Test task - học tiếng anh",
  "description": "Task để test auto status update",
  "priority": "high",
  "estimatedDuration": 420,
  "dailyTargetMin": 60,
  "dailyTargetDuration": 60,
  "deadline": "2026-03-11T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Response sẽ trả về task với status = "todo"

### 2. Get task by ID (verify initial status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Quick update status to "in_progress"
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Expected response:
# {
#   "task": {
#     "id": "...",
#     "title": "Test task - học tiếng anh",
#     "status": "in_progress",
#     ...
#   },
#   "message": "Đã cập nhật trạng thái thành in_progress"
# }

### 4. Update status to "completed"
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### 5. Update status to "cancelled"
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "cancelled"
}

### 6. Update status back to "todo"
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "todo"
}

### 7. Test invalid status (should return 400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "invalid_status"
}

### Expected error response:
# {
#   "message": "Status không hợp lệ. Phải là: todo, in_progress, completed, cancelled"
# }

### 8. Test AI Schedule Plan (auto status update)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/schedule-plan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskIds": ["TASK_ID_HERE"],
  "startDate": "2026-03-07"
}

### Response sẽ trả về schedule với các sessions

### 9. Apply AI Schedule (tasks will auto change to "in_progress")
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/save-ai-schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "schedule": [
    {
      "day": "Thứ Bảy",
      "date": "2026-03-07",
      "tasks": [
        {
          "sessionId": "session_1",
          "taskId": "TASK_ID_HERE",
          "title": "học tiếng anh",
          "priority": "high",
          "suggestedTime": "08:00 - 08:30",
          "reason": "Giờ làm việc hiệu quả",
          "createSubtask": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suggestedOrder": ["TASK_ID_HERE"],
  "personalizationNote": "Test auto status update"
}

### 10. Verify task status changed to "in_progress"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: status should be "in_progress" now

### 11. List all tasks (check status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Test unauthorized access (no token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Expected error response (401):
# {
#   "message": "Chưa đăng nhập"
# }

### 13. Test forbidden access (wrong user)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/OTHER_USER_TASK_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Expected error response (403):
# {
#   "message": "Không có quyền cập nhật task này"
# }

### 14. Full task update (existing endpoint - still works)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "status": "completed",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### This still works! Quick status update is just a shortcut

### 15. Delete test task (cleanup)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### TEST SCENARIOS SUMMARY:
###
### ✓ Create task → status = "todo"
### ✓ Quick update status → status changes immediately
### ✓ AI schedule applied → status auto changes to "in_progress"
### ✓ Invalid status → returns 400 error
### ✓ Unauthorized → returns 401 error
### ✓ Forbidden → returns 403 error
### ✓ Full update still works
###
